Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:05.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不冒险是无法破壳而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:20.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}Lv6？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}听说是第37层吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好像单枪匹马打倒了深区域的层主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:29.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}单枪匹马…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:36.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一般有实力的人都要组大规模的队伍才能打倒的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 不能把自己和她比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}连我都没听说过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}而是华伦斯坦小姐太特别了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}即便只靠近一点 我也想要赶上这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}再来一次 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:08.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么你能这么快变得这么强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一点…也不快 不强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}希…希尔小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我非常想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}洗碗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:26.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}积压了好几天的工作 因为我偷懒…不 休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:30.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}挨米娅大妈的骂 所以作为惩罚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我根本就是无辜受牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:37.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}非常抱歉贝尔先生 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:43.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但不用考虑多余的事也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这个量太恐怖了 我帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:50.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请问 琉小姐以前是冒险者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:01.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是 但都是过去的事了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:04.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有关升级 要怎么做才能升级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}仅靠打倒怪兽就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 仅靠这样还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:15.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要提高功绩 具体就是需要打倒强大的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但 但是能打赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一般来说是难以实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:23.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但之所以能实现就要靠技巧 就是灵活运用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}技巧之类的灵活运用 你还需要稍作加强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}话虽如此 但也并非仅靠这个就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一般来说需要组队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:43.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果你真的想变强 迟早会需要组队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就算一个人不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:50.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要和他人联手互补 就能打败更强的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:59.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}升级的条件 换句话说就是要冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}每个人都是有属于自己冒险的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:08.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}虽然我不知道需要你面对的冒险为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但请你不要把目光移开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}因为你是冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:21.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你所追求的东西恐怕只有在那里才能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:26.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不过我的直觉经常出错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}终于能反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:56.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今天是最后一天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这一周非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也要说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}过得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:17.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是 艾丝小姐也要…呃…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不知道自己是否能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:31.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但一定要做 要追赶上她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}追赶至触手可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:44.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今早和艾丝·华伦某某的特训真的结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:45.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}和预期计划一样 今天起要参加洛基眷族的远征
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗 原来已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}即便如此 这个能力值也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么神明大人 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 状态还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 等我回来再看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}从现在起 启程前往地下城深层的远征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:34.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这次也同样为了避免上层的混杂 分两组行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一组由我带队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}另一组由加雷斯带队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这次赫菲斯托斯眷族的锻造师也会陪同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在第18层汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}从那里一鼓作气到第50层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们的目标别无其他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就是前往未曾到达的领域 第59层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}事情安排妥当了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贪婪的冒险者已经到位了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好戏可能会早开场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:07.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗 让我欣赏一下那孩子的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么了 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 你没察觉到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}总觉得有人在注视着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:36.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不知道 不过这层有点异样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 怪兽的数量少得可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}而且冒险者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}和那天的情形一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们走 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}刚才的声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么米诺陶洛斯会出现在第9层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 我们快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}以我们现在的实力无法与之较量 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:28.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝…贝尔大人 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:08.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:16.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭 火焰箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们说米诺陶洛斯居然出现在这层？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们在第9层遇到了手持巨剑的米诺陶洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难道是那时候的漏网之鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:11:00.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不可能 自那之后一个月内再没有人见过米诺陶洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不论如何 最重要的是你们能平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:05.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其他的冒险者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:13.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在这层腹地惨遭毒手 那个白发小鬼现在可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:14.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等等 我们正在远征途中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}伯特 缇欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 这里暂时拜托你照顾行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}和那时候的情形一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}原来你是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这样下去 迟早会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}必须找机会脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 莉莉快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:16.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:17.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:19.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快点跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:34.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这样就好办了 我也可以逃跑…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}现在逃跑的话 莉莉就活不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}闪躲的话 仅靠敏捷还能撑得住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要多砍一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就算丢脸也好 惨不忍睹也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要能争取到时间就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:40.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:45.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你已经尽全力了 现在由我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}救我？ 又被她搭救？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}又被同样的人 和之前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一次次重复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:00.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果在这里不能重新站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:13.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不伸手攀上高峰 更待何时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}找到艾丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你跑这里来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:32.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不行 我不能再让艾丝·华伦斯坦出手救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:15:00.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今天我第一次冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:18.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在地下城抢夺别人的猎物属于违规行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他就是以前那个番茄小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:26.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那小子搞什么 我深切体会到他和米诺陶洛斯还真是有缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}于是 那时候艾丝搭救了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:34.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}米诺陶洛斯过于想念番茄小鬼 千里迢迢从中层跑来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别开玩笑 伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}确实不想被救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:43.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}而且同样情景一样的惨样再度被那时搭救自己的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}行吗 那孩子Lv1吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}绝对会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你还是别管 缇欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那小子现在想做一个男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}两次都被同一个人搭救 换我的话连死的心都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}拜托你们了 冒险者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}救救贝尔大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}小人族 你还不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}带我们来这里已经到达你的极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要你们出手 一定会有回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要我做什么都行 什么都答应你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}救救贝尔大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:35.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}求求你们…救救…贝尔…贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:39.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}打算出手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:44.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别会错意了 我是不会出手救杂碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:48.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但我更瞧不起欺负弱小的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝让开 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那孩子真的是Lv1？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:06.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一个月前在伯特眼中 那孩子确实是个新手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:07.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这就是属于我的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我想成为 成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好像英雄愿望的童话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}讲述一位少年成长为英雄的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我以前很喜欢那个童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:47.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}美丽 美丽的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那把刀是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}虽是把宝刀 但并不全靠那把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:57.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他靠的是技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:01.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}攻击确实都避开了 但是没有余力反击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}弥诺陶洛斯的肉不容易切开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个魔法不需要咏唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 但是对方不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}下手太轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}岂不是别无他法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还是年轻鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:01.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}居然赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}站着晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:25.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}精神枯竭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}黎贝利亚 那家伙的能力值是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要我去偷看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:50.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那种情况下 不看白不看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是多少 快点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能力全部是S
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔·克朗尼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}尽全力了吧 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:53.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人 我想变强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:02.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这就是我们故事的第一篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
